comment: RHH and LATR show Joseph (TOR) gets into a screening position on Pachulia (DAL), giving him enough room to avoid the contact and absorbing contact when it occurs.

R-Slash Valanciunas (TOR) gets into a screening position on Williams (DAL), giving him enough room to avoid the screen. He takes a wide stance, but firms up over his leg as contact occurs, absorbing the contact in his shoulder (not legs).
After making the pass, Lowry (TOR) turns in front of Nowitzki (DAL) and affects Nowitzki's ability to defend the shot by holding his arm out in front of his path.
Valanciunas (TOR) clamps Williams' (DAL) arm as the shot goes up.
Williams (DAL) pulls Valanciunas (TOR) down to the floor.
LHH and RATR show Dallas is not ready to resume play when the time-out clock reaches 00:00.
Harris (DAL) commits a take foul on Lowry (TOR).
Valanciunas (TOR) allows Powell (DAL) to land safely following his shot attempt.
Valanciunas (TOR) first clamps Matthews (DAL) and then dislodges him while trying to establish post position. Call should have been made sooner, but correct.
Barea (DAL) cleanly strips the ball from Joseph (TOR), getting his hand while it is in contact with the ball.
